name: Tezzy Everydays #4 | Jaws 2 "The Tez Batch" | May 9th, 2021
description: This is the fourth day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I decided to go with a Jaws inspired piece for today. Growing up in the 80's near Revere Beach in Massachusetts, I always had this underlying fear while floating in the freezing cold waters of the Atlantic. The fear of getting snacked on by giant mega predators that you can't see is REAL on the coast of Mass. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
